<p>This document provides a complete guide to training the DETR-based detec=
tion model in GigaCheck. The detection model identifies character-level int=
ervals of AI-generated content within mixed human/AI text, outputting preci=
se boundary annotations rather than document-level classifications.</p>
<p>For document-level classification training, see <a href=3D"https://deepw=
iki.com/ai-forever/gigacheck/4.1-classification-model-training" class=3D"te=
xt-neutral-300 hover:text-neutral-200 hover:underline">Classification Model=
 Training</a>. For details on the DETR architecture itself, see <a href=3D"=
https://deepwiki.com/ai-forever/gigacheck/5.3-detr-detection-architecture" =
class=3D"text-neutral-300 hover:text-neutral-200 hover:underline">DETR Dete=
ction Architecture</a>. For general training configuration parameters, see =
<a href=3D"https://deepwiki.com/ai-forever/gigacheck/4.3-training-configura=
tion" class=3D"text-neutral-300 hover:text-neutral-200 hover:underline">Tra=
ining Configuration</a>.</p>
