<p>The detection training pipeline fine-tunes a pre-trained Mistral-7B mode=
l with a DETR (DEtection TRansformer) head to predict character-level inter=
vals marking AI-generated text spans. Unlike classification training which =
uses LoRA adapters and Deepspeed, detection training employs the full DETR =
architecture with Accelerate for multi-GPU distribution.</p>
